{"type": "article", "id": 18748, "title": "如果你肯把钱烧在袜子上，那说明你是真爱时尚", "description": "或者真爱袜子爱生活，哈哈哈。", "date": "2015-12-11T11:44:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7968, "name": "Coolhunting"}, {"id": 2532, "name": "袜子"}, {"id": 20081, "name": "Kapital"}, {"id": 20082, "name": "Corgi Fair Isle"}, {"id": 20083, "name": "Apolis"}, {"id": 20084, "name": "Marwood + Goodhood"}], "category": 19, "column": 24, "author": 18, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 337, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121458Prta83uVj9olDOk4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<!--?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" standalone=\"no\"?--> <b><a href=\"http://www.coolhunting.com/style/warm-socks-with-style-roundup\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>本</strong></em><em><strong>文</strong></em></a><em><strong>由 Coolhunting 授权《好奇心日报》发布，即使我们允许了也不许转载。</strong></em></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t除了拿来装圣诞节礼物，袜子本身也可以成为礼物的一种。随着一年又一年过去，人们好像越来越喜欢穿有点个性、或是非常个性化的袜子了。寒冬来临，保暖才是关键——不过也用不着牺牲风度。下面 6 双短袜不是为雪上运动准备，而是在更冷的天也很管用的休闲短袜。无论是从厚度、材质、保暖性、舒适性、功能性还是设计风格上看，这些袜子都很耐穿。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121456CZoIY4dDmWJPtURc.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"550\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h1>\r\n\tKapital “梵高”毛粒短袜\r\n</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>日本生产的</span><span> Kapital <a href=\"http://www.hickorees.com/brand/kapital/product/van-gogh-slub-socks-yellow\"><span>“</span><span>梵高</span><span>”</span><span>毛粒短袜</span></a></span><span>（</span><span>41 </span><span>美元），采用厚实的混合纱纺制而成。这个东京品牌早已不限于生产美式牛仔工装类产品了，现在加入了简洁图案的配件，让足上的风格也混搭起来。这双袜子就很别具一格。<span>（上图左）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h1>\r\n\t<span>Corgi Fair Isle </span><span>羊毛混棉短袜</span> \r\n</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>很难不把</span><span> Fair Isle </span><span>针织图案与冬天联系到一块儿，尤其把它用在威尔士传统短袜厂商</span><span> Corgi </span><span>的羊毛混棉产品上时，这无疑会是双理想的应季短袜。这些</span><span> <a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/en-us/mens/corgi/fair-isle-wool-and-cotton-blend-socks/608764?ppv=2\"><span>Fair Isle </span><span>图案羊毛混棉短袜</span></a></span><span>（</span><span>25 </span><span>美元）穿起来毛绒绒的，十分舒适且款式养眼。<span>（上图右）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121457Jw1ADXnM7arCK9ds.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"538\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h1>\r\n\tApolis“羊驼之旅”短袜\r\n</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>羊驼毛制成的灰色短袜与服装可以随意搭配，比如</span><span> Apolis </span><span>的</span><span>“</span><span>羊驼之旅</span><span>”</span><span>短袜（<a href=\"http://store.apolisglobal.com/accessories/alpaca-trek-socks/#navy\"><span>Alpaca Trek Socks</span></a>，</span><span>28 </span><span>美元），它在功能上也是复合型的，不仅温暖舒适，还可以在徒步旅行时穿着。虽说灰色不是什么鲜艳的色彩，不过对那些想告别黑白色袜子的人来说，这也算是个尝试的开端。<span>（上图左）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h1>\r\n\t<span>Marwood + Goodhood </span><span>浸染马海毛袜</span> \r\n</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>英格兰生产、</span><span>Goodhood </span><span>商场专卖的</span><span> Marwood <a href=\"http://goodhoodstore.com/store/18595\"><span>浸染马海毛袜</span></a></span><span>（</span><span>45 </span><span>欧元），将材质的功效最大化，同时保持其独特的极简风格。马海毛是种柔软的兔毛，能起到隔热作用，同时吸湿排汗。它很容易染色，因而可以完美展现浸染工艺的美感。<span>（上图右）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121457Yz8twglxIQXmvDRb.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"539\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h1>\r\n\t<span>Etiquette </span><span>粗花呢罗纹短袜</span> \r\n</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>美利奴羊毛是制作</span><span> Etiquette </span><span>粗花呢罗纹短袜（</span><span>36 </span><span>美元）的理想材质，这款短袜其他方面也颇具特色。沿着袜子方向有条很厚的罗纹，使袜子有足够的弹性与足部贴合，此外还有舒适的罗口防止袜子移位，连脚尖的针脚缝合都精心处理过，整体营造出一个充满活力的枣红色冬季生活片段。（上图左）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h1>\r\n\t<span>Norse Projects Vibeke </span><span>羊绒短袜</span> \r\n</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Norse Projects </span><span>的</span><span> <a href=\"http://www.norsestore.com/commodity/20715-norse-projects-women-vibeke-cashmere\"><span>Vibeke </span><span>羊绒短袜</span></a></span><span>（</span><span>25 </span><span>美元）采用百分之百纯意大利羊绒。饱满的橄榄绿色配合冬季林间般的自然感受。这家丹麦品牌以可靠的品质闻名，尤其在户外服装领域，所以说这些短袜在气温骤降时候也能靠得住。（上图右）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片版权归各品牌所有\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>题图来自 <span><a href=\"http://mansterrain.wordpress.com/2013/12/16/socks/\">wordpress.com</a></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>翻译 Alicia Lee</span> \r\n</p>\n\n"}